summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plats 232E and 233W page 27 and 28 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Meridian Avenue Acres; Hawke's Addition; Erickson's Improved Addition; Burke and Farrar's Licton Springs gardens; all of Homeland Addition; all of Phillips's Addition, Section 31-26-4 and Section 32-26-4.
